  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study of the contribution of ultrasound measurements of the uterine cervix related to the
      calculation of Bishop score. Evaluation of the period between cervical induction and
      delivery. Study of ultrasound data to improve the care of these patients requiring induction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
